<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Order Cancelled</h2>
        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>Your order <strong>#<%= orderId %></strong> has been automatically cancelled because we did not receive payment within the allowed time frame.</p>
        <p>If you'd still like to purchase these items, please place a new order on our website.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
